sequenceDiagram
    title LessJS v0.26.0 — Dev:Fast 零 Bundler SSR 渲染流程

    participant Browser as 🌐 Browser
    participant Deno as 🦕 Deno.serve
    participant Hono as 🔀 Hono Router
    participant SSR as 🧩 SSR Middleware
    participant NavData as 📋 @openelement/content/nav
    participant RouteModule as 📄 Route Module
    participant RenderDSD as 🎨 render-dsd.ts
    participant AdapterLit as 🔌 @openelement/adapter-lit

    Browser->>Deno: GET /docs/getting-started
    Deno->>Hono: fetch(request)

    alt 静态资源 (.js/.css/.svg/.png)
        Hono->>Hono: serveStatic from public/
        Hono-->>Browser: 文件内容 (304 Not Modified)
    else SSR 路由
        Hono->>SSR: 请求路径 /docs/getting-started
        SSR->>SSR: isStaticAsset() → false

        Note over SSR,NavData: SOP-001 成果：纯 ESM，零 virtual: 导入
        SSR->>NavData: import { navTree } from '@openelement/content/nav'
        NavData-->>SSR: NavTree { groups, flatMap }

        SSR->>SSR: findNavItemInTree(navTree, path)
        SSR->>SSR: resolveRouteModule() → modulePath

        SSR->>RouteModule: dynamic import('www/routes/docs/getting-started.ts')
        RouteModule-->>SSR: RouteModule { render(ctx) }

        SSR->>RouteModule: render({ path, query })

        Note over RouteModule,RenderDSD: Lit SSR → DSD 渲染管线
        RouteModule->>RenderDSD: JSX/Lit TemplateResult → HTML
        RenderDSD->>AdapterLit: TemplateResult → string (SSR)
        AdapterLit-->>RenderDSD: HTML with Declarative Shadow DOM
        RenderDSD-->>RouteModule: DSD HTML string

        RouteModule-->>SSR: HTML string

        SSR->>SSR: wrapDocument(html, { path })
        Note over SSR: 注入 headExtras, PWA manifest, color tokens

        SSR-->>Hono: 完整 HTML 文档
        Hono-->>Deno: Response (200, text/html)
        Deno-->>Browser: Full HTML with DSD

        Note over Browser: Declarative Shadow DOM 自动升级
        Note over Browser: Island hydration (eager/idle/visible)

        Browser->>Deno: GET /islands/my-counter.js
        Deno->>Hono: serveStatic dist/client/islands/
        Hono-->>Browser: Island JS chunk
        Note over Browser: customElements.define() → Island 激活
    end

    Note over Browser,AdapterLit: 零 Bundler 模式优势：
    Note over Browser,AdapterLit: 1. 冷启动 < 1s（无 Vite 预构建）
    Note over Browser,AdapterLit: 2. 纯 ESM import，Deno 原生模块图
    Note over Browser,AdapterLit: 3. Source map 直接映射（无 Vite 转换层）
